desc_long								关于这款游戏							Collisions is a relaxing puzzle game set in a beautiful environment. The puzzles vary from one screen to the next: some are easy, others require timing, logic and anticipation. Many puzzles have alternative solutions that only the most cunning players would be able to find!Featuresover 50 physics-based puzzles20 bonuses/alternative solutionsmini-gamesrelaxing soundtrackengaging hints expressed in proverb formsubtle, non-verbal story						
